      <div class="faq-q">What versions are supported? <span class="faq-arr">›</span></div>
      <div class="faq-a">We support 1.8.9, 1.12.2, 1.16.5, 1.18.2, 1.19.4, 1.20.x, and 1.21.4. All versions are included in every plan at no extra cost.</div>
